---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Leadership Cadence — Wychwood Partners" description="Weekly execution rhythm, accountability loops, and leadership team performance.">
  <main class="shell py-14">
    <h1>Leadership cadence</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
      A weekly execution rhythm that sticks: the meeting architecture, decision hygiene, and accountability loops that keep momentum.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="card p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">What it includes</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
          <li>• Weekly exec rhythm</li>
          <li>• KPI review + actions</li>
          <li>• Decision logs</li>
          <li>• Accountability loops</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">When it’s needed</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
          <li>• Meetings without decisions</li>
          <li>• Repeated issues</li>
          <li>• “Everyone is busy”</li>
          <li>• No clear follow-through</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Outcomes</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
          <li>• Better decisions</li>
          <li>• Faster execution</li>
          <li>• Clear ownership</li>
          <li>• Stronger leadership team</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 card p-8">
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold">Want to install a cadence that sticks?</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">We’ll implement the rhythm, then coach the team until it becomes habit.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="mt-5 inline-flex rounded-[var(--radius-lg)] bg-[rgb(var(--brand-anchor))] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white transition hover:opacity-95">Book a call</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
